 Mrs South Africa is not like any other beauty pageant, it aims to empower married women, just like Mrs Mogashoa, through empowerment programmes. The mother of two from Mhluzi is among 100 other semi-finalists in the contest, she is urging residents to vote for her so that she can become a finalist. Simply like the Mrs Tammy Taylor Nails South Africa Facebook page and like her picture, or SMS Khanyisile Mogashoa to 35959. For more information about the contest follow Khanyisile Mogashoa on Facebook.     Parents frustrated by a lack of space in Middelburg schools Traffic officers to appear in court for corruption #TrafficAlert: Two dead in Kranspoort accidents VIDEO: Two perish after truck jack-knifes • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za